{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01TUM44pzNN1nVZFPLxTQxkN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All done. Here's what was wrong and what was fixed:\n\n**Root cause:** The probes had been tightened to values MongoDB with authentication cannot satisfy:\n- `timeoutSeconds: 1` — mongosh + auth handshake takes >1s, causing every probe to time out\n- `initialDelaySeconds: 5/15` — replica set initialization needs much more startup time\n- `failureThreshold: 2` — pods were killed before they had a chance to stabilize\n\n**Fix applied:** Restored to proper values via `kubectl patch`:\n\n| Probe | Setting | Before | After |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| readiness | `initialDelaySeconds` | 5 | 30 |\n| readiness | `timeoutSeconds` | 1 | 5 |\n| readiness | `failureThreshold` | 2 | 6 |\n| liveness | `initialDelaySeconds` | 15 | 60 |\n| liveness | `timeoutSeconds` | 1 | 5 |\n| liveness | `failureThreshold` | 2 | 10 |\n\n**Result:** All 3 pods are `1/1 Ready` with 1 PRIMARY (`mongodb-replica-2`) and 2 SECONDARY members."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":519,"cache_read_input_tokens":33722,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":519},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4087f162-5de9-4649-af72-ef27c26d6bcd","uuid":"3c26ef9c-7901-4c4a-a250-2c94273af515","request_id":"req_011CcfskcgyS7jYdEp3eszp1"}
